INSERT INTO mc_product_langs VALUES('2519','1010','1','Samsung ST150F (16.2 Megapixel, Digital Still Camera, White)','Share your best pictures in style with the ST150. Instantly email or upload high quality photos to your social networks, right from your camera.\n\nInstant Wireless Sharing\n\nInstantly send quality photos to social networks like Facebook or email them to a small group of peopleâdirectly from the camera. The dedicated DIRECT LINK hot key helps you quickly connect to Wi-Fi networks. Access your uploaded content on supported connected devices.\n\nInstant Saving\n\nSimultaneously send every picture you take to your mobile phone via Wi-Fi connectionâto make backing up and sharing your high-quality photos easy.\n\nCustomize and Edit\n\nEven if you\'re not ready for your close-up, you can still create the perfect social network profile picture. Beauty Palette lets you choose from seven different makeup looks that help you change photos instantly.\n\nHybrid Touch Display\n\nThe Hybrid Touch Display offers two options: use the 5-way button to quickly move the cursor and intuitively navigate the menu and make selections. Alternately, when you want to enter text simply input the characters on the touch screen. It couldnât be easier.','','1');
INSERT INTO mc_product_langs VALUES('2520','1011','1','Canon EOS 700D 18-55mm Lens Kit ','The Canon EOS 700D is a DSLR camera that comes with a huge list of advanced features. Starting with the 18MP Hybrid CMOS AF sensor, this camera can let you shoot high resolution images that can be enlarged and recomposed by cropping without losing detail. This black camera delivers Full HD 1080p video recording that accurately portrays the exact ambiance and emotions of a particular scene. It employs the Hybrid AF technology to ensure that your subject remains in focus continuously, irrespective of the lighting conditions or the movement of the subject. When you want to record videos in complete silence, you can use the Movie Servo AF mode. It works with compatible STM lenses, and ensures that the camera does not make any noise when focusing.\n\n18MP Hybrid CMOS AF Sensor,Full HD 1080p Recording,Fast AF Performance,3 Inch Vari Angle Clear View LCD II Touch Screen Monitor,Touch Screen Control,Scene Intelligent Auto,Creative Photography.','','1');
INSERT INTO mc_product_langs VALUES('2521','1012','1','Nikon D5100 18-55mm Lens Kit (16.2 Megapixels, DSLR Camera, Black)','Explore a new dimension of photography with the Nikon D5100, a high end DLSR camera that comes with loads of features. It features a 16.2MP CMOS sensor that captures even the tiniest details in any scene. Additionally, the EXPEED 2 image processor quickens up the process of images being captured and processed, enabling you to capture Full HD images at high speeds. The innovative Vari Angle LCD monitor swivels away from the camera body, allowing you to easily capture photos from awkward angles such as ground level, waist level, or over the head. The 921,000 dot LCD monitor also enables you to compose your shots accurately, and view all the recorded photos and videos with good detail. The D5100 provides you with a multitude of special effects to choose from. These effects can go a long way in making your photos look more fun and interesting. The 11 point AF system of this camera continuously tracks your subject if it is moving within the frame and ensures that it never loses focus, allowing for razor sharp photos.\n\nCreative Photography,Vari Angle LCD Monitor,Fun and Interesting Effects,Full HD 1080p D Movie with Audio Recording,Stunning Image Quality,High Speed Shooting,Sharp and Precise AF System,Automatic Flash,Compatibility with NIKKOR Lenses.\n\n','','1');
