d precise Live View and Movie shooting. Versatile Scene Modes lets you choose from Portrait, Landscape, Child, Sports, Close-up or Night Portrait for stunning results in otherwise challenging conditions. The Nikon D7000 has a variety of really wonderful features that inspire you and provide you with new ideas to shoot glamour and creative shots, and it gives you amazing and professional results that make you so proud! It is well suited to professional photographers, and even to beginners with creative photography talents. Itâs one of the best DSLR cameras you could ever own!\n\n','','1');
